com.asgoc.common.code.json

Class ConcreteJSONManipulator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.asgoc.common.code.json.ConcreteJSONManipulator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JSONManipulatorAdaptor

    class ConcreteJSONManipulator
extends java.lang.Object
implements JSONManipulatorAdaptor
    Class that serves as a wrapper for the JSON creation and manipulation library. The class is an implementation of the JSONManipulaotr interface. It provides an interface only to a small portion of the library that is required. Most of the methods return the instance of the JSONManipulatorAdaptor used to invoke them to allow nesting of calls.
    Author:
    Kaartic Sivaraam
